e="preserve">Josep Corominas i Busqueta (24 March 1939 – 30 December 2020) was a Spanish physician and politician. He was a member of the Congress of Deputies from 1989 and 2000. He also was Grand Master of the Spain's Grand Lodge from 2002 and 2006.
Corominas i Busqueta died in Barcelona on 30 December 2020 at the age of 81.
